creator: Vowell's
descriptionHtml:
The Vowell's Marketplace and Vowell's Cashsaver Rewards app is the easiest way for our loyal shoppers to shop online, receive savings every time they come into the store! Vowell's Marketplace and Vowell's Cashsaver Rewards app puts shopping, savings and rewards at one place and click away. Store Pickup and Delivery right from the app. It's as simple 1, 2, 3:

1. Get the Vowell's Marketplace and Vowell's Cashsaver app.
2. Adding coupons and specials to your shopping list, and
3. Presenting loyalty card to cashier to scan at check out.

For online shopping, add items to cart, choose store pick or delivery, pick delivery/pickup time slot and complete the order payment.

Claim as many coupons as you want with one simple scan! No more searching through mailers or printing out emails, Vowell's Marketplace and Vowell's Cashsaver are bringing rewards right to your mobile device!
You can view your purchase history and track order status in the app.
descriptionShort: The easy way to receive customized Coupons and collect Rewards!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Online shopping is now enabled. User Interface and functionality have been enhanced. For online shopping, users can add items to the cart, choose between store pickup or delivery, select a delivery or pickup time slot, and complete the order payment.
